### ShadCN Components

- All UI components must use ShadCN
- Component usage path should be: `/components/ui`
- Component installation command: `npx shadcn@latest add [component-name]`
  - Note: `npx shadcn-ui@latest add` is deprecated. Use `npx shadcn@latest add` instead

### Icons

- All icons must use Lucide React
- Icon import format: `import { IconName } from "lucide-react"`
- Example: `import { Search, Menu } from "lucide-react"`

### Component Structure

- Components should be placed under `/components`
- UI components should be placed under `/components/ui`
- Page components should be placed under `/app`

### Best Practices

- TypeScript strict mode must be enabled
- Components must be reusable 